    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and has been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, showroom shine and is completely free of any scratches, chips, or dents. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with leather that remains supple and all electronics functioning perfectly. This car has been garage-kept, regularly serviced, and truly represents the pinnacle of its model's condition.",
